{"tid":2412909,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姜丹尼爾罹憂鬱、恐慌症：活得不像人　動念隱退「失去生活目標」","createTime":"2021-02-18T10:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T04:22:36.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d242e2bf6d0289409733d40db40f7c4867a9e82a","tid":2412909,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"南韓歌手姜丹尼爾透過實境選秀出道，曾組團Wanna One，人氣紅遍亞洲各國，怎料，團體合約到期解散後，他與前經紀公司發生合約糾紛，人生面臨前所未有的低潮，連演藝活動都受到影響。花了很多時間才重新振作，他17日出演談話性節目《黃金漁場》，坦言2019年一口氣罹患憂鬱症、恐慌障礙，對於生活絲毫沒有慾望，狀況一度惡化。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5457/d5457751.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5457%2Fd5457751.jpg&h=cfa97285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲姜丹尼爾在節目上坦言2019年罹憂鬱、恐慌症「活得不像人而是動物」。（圖／翻攝自MBC）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n姜丹尼爾2019年曾一度因憂鬱症、恐慌障礙中斷演藝活動，他17日談起這段黑暗的時光，承認對於生活沒有慾望，「活下去的目標意識消失，活得不像人而是動物，就像是為了不死而活，這個事情（演藝圈活動）跟我不太合，連放棄都想過了，就這樣陷入惡循環，憂鬱症也變嚴重了。」當時曾經動念隱退。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5457/d5457754.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5457%2Fd5457754.jpg&h=87497ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼姜丹尼爾當時動念隱退，最後靠寫歌克服。（圖／翻攝自MBC）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5457/d5457752.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5457%2Fd5457752.jpg&h=41267566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然而，當看到其他歌手的舞台與歌曲，姜丹尼爾依舊有「想要站在舞台上的熱情」，於是找到了對抗憂鬱的辦法，當感到辛苦時，他就會以寫歌的方式抒發心情，此次帶著新作品《PARANOIA》回歸，他表示：「這首歌是我在感到困難的時候寫的，歌詞意境，因此歌詞跟主題很黑暗，題目是偏執症，害怕我自己傷害到別人，但我傷害我自己是不是也是一種偏執症，所以寫了這首歌。」所幸姜丹尼爾透過音樂將憂鬱心情、狀態都調整好，當天也在節目上展露出6塊腹肌，展露笑容。"},{"pid":"84e739b8abad563b88105b52902d8600c2fd22b1","tid":2412909,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:28:22.000Z","msg":"同定仔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ef21fdc84d9c09b15c785be6d061e827fdc26f","tid":2412909,"uid":224479,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:46:55.000Z","msg":"一晚屌G效幾多劑？"},{"pid":"a6d099b8ab2003f5e08d92503fb2b470dc247c70","tid":2412909,"uid":384468,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:58:03.000Z","msg":"快撚d死啦"},{"pid":"e96e82f0eb8cdb3116cb2cb6e40fe4eb55dde36a","tid":2412909,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:16:18.000Z","msg":"典解唔係希澈老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83a7cc5bf5619795715e2c3f47d28b2fe20f5af","tid":2412909,"uid":215249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:18:46.000Z","msg":"覓腸慘D 定紋身佬慘D"},{"pid":"962c5a236e6ab53ab98761eab4c0dbc1cd37a9a8","tid":2412909,"uid":136770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:35:28.000Z","msg":"比牙效採陽採得太犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e86330316524cf5e5c5494e5913e2c31355941b","tid":2412909,"uid":43061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:36:44.000Z","msg":"大山婆太大食?"},{"pid":"55866376c1a1187dd398bca617d2bc758c5101db","tid":2412909,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T23:08:00.000Z","msg":"咁慘都有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d81ac0047970234703f896866d8dd2942401d9","tid":2412909,"uid":253320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T23:10:26.000Z","msg":"扮晒野咁"},{"pid":"659398ca29f332c4097e42023b8bc1b091aba7ce","tid":2412909,"uid":34643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T23:29:54.000Z","msg":"咁又係, 巨乳都玩到厭, 重有咩人生意義"},{"pid":"a251db43bc6374613f3a3aeb85c6797d43601329","tid":2412909,"uid":211461,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T23:33:26.000Z","msg":"玩大波妹狂揸巨乳 乳交夾腸奶爆 學人講抑鬱 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj